flowchart TD
    subgraph Hardware[Hardware: Ubuntu 26.04 / AMD RX 9060 XT 16GB]
        ROCm[ROCm 7.2 Drivers] --> GPU[GPU: 32 CUs, 35°C]
    end

    subgraph Inference[Inference Engine]
        Ollama[Ollama v0.31.1<br>Port 11434] --> LLM[qwen3:8b / tinyllama]
        Ollama --> Embed[nomic-embed-text]
    end

    subgraph Memory[Memory Stores]
        Vault[Obsidian Vault<br>~/nova-vault<br>Git-backed (10 commits)]
        LanceDB[LanceDB<br>~/.hermes/lancedb<br>Vector Store]
    end

    subgraph Tools[Manual Tools (nova-tools)]
        VaultOps[vault_operations.py<br>Read/Write/Append]
        IndexMem[index_memory.py<br>Index/Search]
    end

    subgraph Interface[Human Interface]
        ObsidianApp[Obsidian App<br>Syzygy Theme]
        Dashboard[NovaHub Dashboard<br>Port 3000<br>Read-only Status View]
    end

    %% Current Relations (Siloed)
    ObsidianApp -->|Human writes manually| Vault
    Dashboard -.->|Reads DB only| Vault
    User[Bo] -->|Runs manually| Tools
    Tools -->|Reads/Writes| Vault
    Tools -->|Indexes/Searches| LanceDB
    Tools -->|Queries| Ollama

